OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BProgram information           BPATCH2  
OL,7,                              B(Acorn)  
OL,8,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,9,BThe PATCH2 program is provided for BBC 
OL,10,BMicro users running the TFS ROM.       
OL,12,BRefer to the Acorn Teletext System user
OL,13,Bguide for downloading instructions.    
OL,15,BOnce downloaded typeG*DISCBorG*TAPEBand
OL,16,BRUN. The screen will be corrupted for a
OL,17,Bmoment, and TSOFT will be created on   
OL,18,Bdisc or tape.                          
OL,20,BTo use TSOFT, typeG*RUN TSOFTBthen use 
OL,21,G*LOADBorGCHAINBto download telesoftware
OL,22,Bfrom the selected page number.         
OL,23,B```````````````````````````````````1/4`
OL,24,ABBC indexBZX SpectrumCSuperPage58FIndex
