OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BProgram information:         BTEST     
OL,7,                           B(ZXGuesser) 
OL,8,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,9,BProbably the most boring telesoftware  
OL,10,Bprogram ever created for the BBC micro.
OL,12,BThe classic BASIC Hello World program. 
OL,14,BIt would be quicker to type it in by   
OL,15,Byourself than to download it!          
OL,20,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,21,BTFS users must use PATCH2 to download  
OL,22,Bthis exciting piece of software...     
OL,23,B```````````````````````````````````2/4`
OL,24,ABBC indexBZX SpectrumCSuperPage58FIndex
PN,45303
SC,0003
RE,0
FL,450,460,106,101,8ff,450
