OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BProgram information:         BMONITOR  
OL,7,                           B(ZXGuesser) 
OL,8,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,9,BA teletext signal monitor utility for  
OL,10,Bthe Acorn Teletext Adapter.            
OL,12,BDisplays a live view of the packet data
OL,13,Breceived by the adapter on either field
OL,14,Bof the television signal.              
OL,16,BThis program does not use any ROM calls
OL,17,Bso is compatible with both TFS and ATS.
OL,20,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,21,BTFS users must use PATCH2 to download. 
OL,22,BSave withG*SAVE MONITOR 2DC0 2FF7      
OL,23,B```````````````````````````````````3/4`
