OL,5,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,6,BProgram information:         BDATACST  
OL,7,                           B(ZXGuesser) 
OL,8,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,9,BA demonstration datacast reception tool
OL,10,Bwhich displays all messages received on
OL,11,Ba particular datachannel and address.  
OL,13,BThis program calls the ATS ROM, however
OL,14,Bit includes a patching routine to make 
OL,15,Bthe necessary changes for TFS users.   
OL,20,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,21,BTFS users must use PATCH2 to download. 
OL,22,BSave withG*SAVE DATACST 2400 2852 2840 
OL,23,B```````````````````````````````````4/4`
